---
import SectionLine from "../ui/SectionLine.astro";
import Container from "../layout/Container.astro";
---

<section class="relative w-full mt-28 overflow-hidden">
  <SectionLine />

  <!-- Full-width image background with all content layered on top -->
  <div class="relative w-full min-h-[900px] flex flex-col">
    <!-- Background Image (full section) -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full">
      <img
        src="/images/abouttv.png"
        alt="About us"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-[0.35]"
      />
      <!-- Gradient overlays -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent">
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/70 via-black/20 to-transparent"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Top: About Us heading + button (aligned with container) -->
    <Container class="relative z-10 pt-24 pb-12">
      <p
        class="text-[14px] tracking-[0.3em] font-medium text-white/40 uppercase mb-6"
      >
        <span class="text-zinc-500">/05</span> ABOUT
      </p>
      <h2
        class="text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[88px] leading-[1] font-heading font-medium tracking-tighter text-white mb-12"
      >
        About us
      </h2>

      <!-- 2-part button (Figma style) -->
      <button class="flex items-stretch group cursor-pointer">
        <div
          class="bg-brand px-10 py-5 text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[14px] group-hover:bg-brand-hover transition-colors"
        >
          More about us
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-brand border-l border-black/10 px-5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-brand-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="black"
            stroke-width="3"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
            <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
    </Container>

    <!-- Spacer -->
    <div class="flex-grow"></div>

    <!-- Bottom: 3 columns with transparent BG, text gray -> white on hover -->
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full border-t border-dashed border-white/15">
      <Container>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Col 1 -->
          <div class="p-10 lg:p-16 flex flex-col gap-8 group cursor-default">
            <p class="text-[15px] font-bold text-zinc-600 tracking-wider">
              /01
            </p>
            <div
              class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-brand transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-20"
            >
            </div>
            <p
              class="text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.6] font-sans text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500 font-medium"
            >
              HumbleBeeAI Academy exists because <span class="italic"
                >"knowing"</span
              > is not the same as <span class="italic"
                >"being able to deliver."</span
              > Resumes and short interviews often miss what matters: consistency,
              coachability, and real output quality.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Col 2 -->
          <div
            class="p-10 lg:p-16 border-l border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-8 group cursor-default"
          >
            <p class="text-[15px] font-bold text-zinc-600 tracking-wider">
              /02
            </p>
            <div
              class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-brand transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-20"
            >
            </div>
            <p
              class="text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.6] font-sans text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500 font-medium"
            >
              So we built a full-time, mentor-reviewed environment that trains
              and measures those traits through real work. Students follow
              deadlines, reviews, documentation standards, and iterative
              improvement - then graduate with evidence of capability, not just
              learning completion.
              <br /><br />
              The outcome is simple: proof-of-skill you can demonstrate, plus an evaluation
              record shaped through <span
                class="underline decoration-brand underline-offset-8">RISE</span
              >.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Col 3 -->
          <div
            class="p-10 lg:p-16 border-l border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-8 group cursor-default"
          >
            <p class="text-[15px] font-bold text-zinc-600 tracking-wider">
              /03
            </p>
            <div
              class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-brand transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-20"
            >
            </div>
            <p
              class="text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] leading-[1.6] font-sans text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500 font-medium"
            >
              And we take a clear position on what modern engineering requires:
              AI is the new horsepower. The people who thrive won't be those who
              merely "use tools," but those who can ride AI with control and
              responsibility - understanding data, training choices, ethics, and
              real-world application.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </div>
  </div>

  <SectionLine />
</section>
